snippet.title: Psychofinger - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the Psychofinger trailer to see gameplay as you take on hordes of enemies in this finger-shootin’ roguelike FPS. Psychofinger will be available on PC.

Survive hordes of ghosts in this FPS-roguelite. Become an agent at the Department of Metaphysical Investigations and unveil the mystery of an old church. Choose items that will upgrade your character, fight bosses and unlock new hand gestures.
